data.description:
Join us for an organizing party supporting Elizabeth Warren for President. We’ll be gathering at Old Crow Smokehouse in River North to talk about Elizabeth’s vision for real, structural change in this country and start getting our community organized for Elizabeth. 

We'll have lots of information on how to get involved with the campaign, including opportunities to support the campaign in Iowa. 

No donation is required to attend, and the campaign is not asking for one -- but Thomas Day, one of the organizers, is asking all attendees to support the campaign with a few bucks. Senator Warren's campaign is not accepting any money at all from PACs or lobbyists, so support from regular folks like you helps a great deal. Please consider a donation to the Warren for President campaign, and even better, set it to automatically renew each month!

Please donate here: elizabethwarren.com/partydonate
